{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"09123da1-88aa-402a-be0d-39620b4501e0","content":"There's no workflow file in the current directory, so here's a general guide for the migration:\n\n### Key changes to switch to NuGet Trusted Publishing (OIDC)\n\n**1. NuGet.org setup (one-time)**\n- Go to **nuget.org → Manage Packages → Trusted Publishers**\n- Add a new GitHub Actions publisher, specifying your **repo owner**, **repo name**, **workflow filename**, and optionally an **environment name**\n\n**2. Workflow changes**\n\nAdd `id-token: write` permission and remove the API key:\n\n```yaml\njobs:\n  publish:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    # If you configured an environment on nuget.org:\n    environment: nuget-publish\n    permissions:\n      contents: read\n      id-token: write   # Required for OIDC token\n\n    steps:\n      - uses: actions/checkout@v4\n\n      # ... build & pack steps ...\n\n      - name: Push to NuGet\n        run: >\n          dotnet nuget push **/*.nupkg\n          --source https://api.nuget.org/v3/index.json\n```\n\n**3. What to remove**\n- Delete `secrets.NUGET_API_KEY` from your repo settings\n- Remove any `--api-key ${{ secrets.NUGET_API_KEY }}` flags from `dotnet nuget push`\n\n**How it works:** GitHub Actions mints a short-lived OIDC token. The `dotnet` CLI automatically sends it to NuGet.org, which validates it against your trusted publisher policy — no long-lived secret needed.\n\n> **Note:** Trusted publishing requires `dotnet` SDK **8.0.400+** or **9.0.100+**. If you pin an older SDK, update it.\n\nWould you like me to create a sample workflow file?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"361cd4ab-77a6-4f17-9534-f18dc3b7dacd","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The repository appears to be empty. The user is asking a general question about switching from NuGet API key-based publishing to OIDC trusted publishing in GitHub Actions. Let me provide guidance based on my knowledge.","outputTokens":490,"requestId":"B444:328887:787DB49:83DF193:69F156DF"},"id":"885662b8-3939-41f1-8062-d08adbc3beab","timestamp":"2026-04-29T00:55:07.866Z","parentId":"a19fc289-8742-4f9d-8877-0fc210cd9211"}
